## ğŸ¢ **7. Sovereign Azure Regions**

| Geography         | Region Name                  | Managed By             | Purpose                           |
| ----------------- | ---------------------------- | ---------------------- | --------------------------------- |
| **United States** | US Gov Virginia, US Gov Iowa | Microsoft (for US Gov) | For government agencies only      |
| **China**         | China East, China North      | Operated by 21Vianet   | Meets Chinaâ€™s data residency laws |

